data.crew_result:
To use the system, please provide your file details in the following JSON format:

{
  "file_path": "<your_file_path>",
  "file_type": "<pdf|csv|txt>"
}

Once submitted, the system will read the entire content of your document and display it here. For example, if you uploaded a TXT file with the following content:

-----------------------------------------------------
Title: Sample Document
Content:
Line 1: Welcome to our processing system.
Line 2: This file has been successfully uploaded.
Line 3: All content is displayed below for further processing.
Line 4: Thank you for using our service!
-----------------------------------------------------

the complete output would be exactly as shown above. Please replace the sample text with your actual document when uploading.
